SUMMARY:ShopRite Food Collection
DESCRIPTION:Temple Ner Tamid hosts a monthly food drive to benefit the Human Needs Food Pantry\, collecting donations from shoppers at the Brookdale ShopRite (1409 Broad Street in Bloomfield). Our food drives have always been a major charitable resource for the pantry\, which is serving many more food-insecure families since the start of the pandemic. \nWe’re looking for volunteers to request donations at the entrance or receive donated items at the exit. The final shift includes driving to the food pantry in Montclair to help unload the truck. \nClick here to volunteer!
URL:https://nertamid.org/event/shoprite-food-collection-2/2026-03-15/
CATEGORIES:Volunteer Opportunities
END:VEVENT
